ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAgreement for the Sharing of Visa and Immigration Information between Canada and the United States of America
PrecisOrder authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs, or a delegate, to SIGN, on behalf of the Governement of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT TO AMEND THE AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA FOR THE SHARING OF VISA AND IMMIGRATION INFORMATION.
